{"tid":1758968,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"諗番起自己畀人話做過《校園備胎》","createTime":"2019-11-27T11:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T19:04:46.000Z","uid":342367,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55ffd20a27ec0026075dd821f7ca1b118751d23c","tid":1758968,"uid":342367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學都係正正常常有bast friends, 一讀中學就比人暗地話你係備胎。最傷心嘅係你中學最撚friend嘅best friends 都喺大家面前認我係佢私人備胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源一路都唔覺得自己係備胎，直到讀中三，學業越嚟越好，跟住就開始有假Best friends,叫我教佢嗰樣嗰樣，提佢帶個樣嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就咁撚樣過咗三年。直到某一日，去去下厠所聽到個best friends喺廁所嗰到同B,C,D同學講《其實我一直當佢（我）係備胎，唔係因為佢（我）讀書好我先唔想一齊玩，佢（我）個樣係生得幾靚標準樣啦~但都唔夠我（bf）靚，校花一定非我莫屬啦。》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一聽完當堂喊出嚟（好細聲）， 其實我唔係在意佢講靚同唔靚嘅關係，而重點係因為你有目的先嚟同我玩~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心諗點解佢咁講，係咪想攞個威啫？我頂唔順嗰晚同bf攤牌, 佢仲喺度扮白蓮花博人同情~ 唔使講大家都知結果係點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後有我讀書有佢威，最後辛辛苦苦捱到放榜嗰一日，睇見佢嘅仆街樣真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 最後好似聽人講佢死死地去台灣叩門讀大學，我就係香港過我嘅快樂日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小小補充<br />\n之前佢係為錢拍拖，一知道自己要去台灣讀書即刻同香港男友分手不出兩日識咗一個新男友係ig公開po肉照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴打絲打有冇同等嘅經歷啦，但嗰陣時畀佢搞到心理情緒都好影響。依家見返中學同學都有一種莫名嘅尷尬但又算玩得埋<br />\n。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4574b0055e9182b6593cf144da949d15f831ff2c","tid":1758968,"uid":154131,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:23:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9871434cc6aff3ad6942f743ad2e1224a58aa6c6","tid":1758968,"uid":181819,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:17:34.000Z","msg":"樓主新移民。block得"},{"pid":"b5d0ed37b73e7bc2efbc03bff7b085856e409f9b","tid":1758968,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"女人真係麻煩"},{"pid":"5dc0809b8dade9aa02730c91417f6c63443f901a","tid":1758968,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5d0ed37b73e7bc2efbc03bff7b085856e409f9b","tid":1758968,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"女人真係麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T19:04:46.000Z","msg":"都係男人好啲."}]}